' Robotics with the Boe-Bot - HaltUnderBrightLight.bs2
' Full speed forward until bright light makes phototransistor circuit's
' output voltage exceed 1.4 V, resulting in IN6=1
' {$STAMP BS2}
' {$PBASIC 2.5}
FREQOUT 4, 2000, 3000
DEBUG "Program running... "
DO UNTIL IN6 = 1
PULSOUT 13, 850
PULSOUT 12, 650
PAUSE 20
LOOP